@Node "From Author" "CopyLockDecoder.guide/From author"

  CopyLockDecoder is written in assembly language using Devpac v3.14. It
  was tested on Amiga 1200 + Blizzard IV 50 MHz + 16 MB Fast Ram + 2.5 GB
  Caviar HDD + CD Rom * 4.

